Huawei’s MateBook 14 is taking the laptop industry by storm thanks to its impressive performance and versatility. It offers peak performance and features for every situation – including remote working, watching videos, and surfing the Internet. Click here to buy the Huawei MateBook 14. Huawei’s MateBook 14 uses a 2K FullView display that leads the 14-inch laptop market. It boasts a 90% screen-to-body ration and supports 10-point multi-touch functionality – something you usually only see on high-end PCs. This multi-touch display allows you to take screenshots by swiping down with three fingers, and can even convert screenshot text into an editable format. This market-leading display is then hosted in an aluminum alloy body that looks and feels great thanks to the advanced sandblasting process it goes through. Between the crisp FullView display and this sleek body, the Huawei MateBook 14 leads the way in laptop design. The MateBook 14 boasts an 11th-generation Intel Core processor that offers high-end power for all your work tasks and home use cases. This powerful processor is supported by up to 16GB RAM and a 512GB NVMe PCIe SSD to offer all of the performance benefits you need out of a laptop. Connectivity was another chief consideration when designing this laptop, and it supports the latest Wi-Fi 6 standard for a faster and more stable Internet connection. You can also use Huawei Share to improve your experience through the easy wireless transfer of files between your laptop and your other Huawei devices. These impressive features are powered by a 56Wh battery and intelligent energy-saving management software, meaning you get up to 12 hours of battery life. Overheating is not an issue, either, as the MateBook 14 uses a customer shark fin fan and dual heat pipe design to maintain the temperature of your laptop within peak operating levels at all times. This amazing laptop is available from the Huawei online store for just R24,999, or from Incredible Connection, Takealot, Vodacom, and MTN. If you are looking for a laptop at a lower price point, the Huawei MateBook D15 i3 is the perfect device for you. This 15.6-inch laptop uses an Intel Core i3 processor for great performance and boasts an impressive FHD display, along with all-day battery-life. This means it checks all of the boxes for a multi-purpose laptop. The Huawei MateBook D15 i3 laptop is available from the Huawei online store for just R10,999, and is the obvious choice if you are shopping for an affordable PC that can do everything. If you purchase either the MateBook 14 or the MateBook D15 i3 from the Huawei online store, you will also get a free backpack, Bluetooth mouse, and VIP service – valued at a combined R2,997.